<emphasis id="85FA4B05507EFFC9C29AFE93FB48FEB4" box="[977,1224,312,334]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="134">Acantoxyura armata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="D31FEAE6507EFFC9C597FE93FAECFEB4" author="Pace R" box="[1244,1388,312,334]" pageId="51" pageNumber="134" pagination="187 - 205" refId="ref38934" refString="Pace R. 1987. Aleocharinae dell'isola della Guadalupa (Antille) (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). Folia Entomologica Hungarica 48: 187 - 205." type="journal article" year="1987">Pace (1987)</bibRefCitation>
